snippet.title: Creepy Doom WADs - 7869.wad (VIDEO REMAKE)
snippet.description:
This is a remake of an old video that was deleted off of YouTube. Go here for more information: http://fav.me/da7hpii
___________________________________

We played a lot of crappy Doom WADs, but we’re going to do a creepy Doom WAD for once! This one’s a real scary one, and it’s based off a Creepypasta story!

Go here for 7869.wad:
http://www.mediafire.com/file/zc85699mptcx3i5/7869-old.wad

Go here for the Creepypasta story that this WAD is based on:
http://web.archive.org/web/20130518152556/http://creepypasta.wikia.com/wiki/DOOM_Lost_Wad

Credits:
Recorded With - Fraps
Maps Made With - Slade3 and Paint.net
Source Port Used - Skulltag
Movie Made With - Windows Live Movie Maker

Music:
"Opening To Hell" from Doom II (MAP30)

The track was composed by Robert "Bobby" Prince
